trans-unit.source: Configures a service credential.
trans-unit.target: Configura uma credencial de serviço.

trans-unit.source: Use this class to specify the credential for the service such as an X.509 certificate.
trans-unit.target: Utilize esta classe para especificar a credencial para o serviço, tais como um certificado x.&509;.

trans-unit.source: Also, use this class to specify the authentication model for various client credentials such as user name and password validation.
trans-unit.target: Além disso, utilize esta classe para especificar o modelo de autenticação para várias credenciais do cliente, tais como a validação de nome e palavra-passe do utilizador.

trans-unit.source: This class is used as a parameter in the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.SecurityBindingElement.BuildChannelListenerCore%2A> method, by methods of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.ServiceCredentialsSecurityTokenManager>, and is returned by the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.Credentials%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Esta classe é utilizada como um parâmetro no <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.SecurityBindingElement.BuildChannelListenerCore%2A>método, pelos métodos do <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.ServiceCredentialsSecurityTokenManager>e é devolvido pelo <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.Credentials%2A?displayProperty=fullName>propriedade.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.Credentials%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.ServiceCredentialsSecurityTokenManager> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.SecurityBindingElement.BuildChannelListenerCore%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can specify a client certificate authentication model using the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.ClaimTypes.Authentication%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Pode especificar um através do modelo de autenticação do certificado de cliente a <xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.ClaimTypes.Authentication%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Claims.ClaimTypes.Authentication%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use this class to specify whether to allow anonymous Windows users access by setting the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.WindowsServiceCredential.AllowAnonymousLogons%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Utilizar esta classe para especificar se pretende permitir o acesso de utilizadores anónimos Windows definindo a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.WindowsServiceCredential.AllowAnonymousLogons%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.WindowsServiceCredential.AllowAnonymousLogons%2A>

trans-unit.source: Also, use this class to specify whether to include a group information to which users belong in the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Policy.AuthorizationContext> by setting the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.WindowsServiceCredential.IncludeWindowsGroups%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Além disso, utilize esta classe para especificar se pretende incluir informações de um grupo ao qual os utilizadores pertencem a <xref:System.IdentityModel.Policy.AuthorizationContext>definindo a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.WindowsServiceCredential.IncludeWindowsGroups%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.WindowsServiceCredential.IncludeWindowsGroups%2A> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Policy.AuthorizationContext>
